    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a solid choice for a reliable daily driver. The exterior paint still holds a deep shine, though upon close inspection, you will notice some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, with the upholstery showing only minimal wear on the driver's side bolster. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a complete service history, ensuring that the next owner can drive away with confidence in its performance and longevity.",
